#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.12:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Balavagga "
msgstr "2. Powers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: sekhabalaaggasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Kūṭasutta "
msgstr "12. Peak "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.10, sc1
msgctxt "an5.12:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, sekhabalāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five powers of a trainee. "

msgctxt "an5.12:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.12:1.3"
msgid "Saddhābalaṃ, hirībalaṃ, ottappabalaṃ, vīriyabalaṃ, paññābalaṃ—"
msgstr "The powers of faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an5.12:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca sekhabalāni. "
msgstr "These are the five powers of a trainee. "

msgctxt "an5.12:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ sekhabalānaṃ etaṃ aggaṃ etaṃ saṅgāhikaṃ etaṃ saṅghātaniyaṃ, yadidaṃ paññābalaṃ. "
msgstr "Of these five powers of a trainee, the power of wisdom is the chief. It holds and binds everything together. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.12:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa etaṃ aggaṃ etaṃ saṅgāhikaṃ etaṃ saṅghātaniyaṃ, yadidaṃ kūṭaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s like a bungalow. The roof-peak is the chief point, which holds and binds everything together. "

msgctxt "an5.12:2.2"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, imesaṃ pañcannaṃ sekhabalānaṃ etaṃ aggaṃ etaṃ saṅgāhikaṃ etaṃ saṅghātaniyaṃ, yadidaṃ paññābalaṃ. "
msgstr "In the same way, of these five powers of a trainee, the power of wisdom is the chief. It holds and binds everything together. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.12:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an5.12:3.2"
msgid "‘saddhābalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalena, hirībalena … ottappabalena … vīriyabalena … paññābalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalenā’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will have the trainee’s powers of faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom.’ "

msgctxt "an5.12:3.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.12:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
